{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban school exclusions after the Covid-19 pandemic",
        "additional_details": "We feel it is imperative to offer children and young people (and their families) support, consistency and understanding without the threat of removing them from their peers, their teachers/support staff and their means of education... which will further damage life chances and mental/ emotional health.\r\n \r\nWe want every school to \"give all children the chance to thrive academically, emotionally and socially\", as called for in the Timpson review of school exclusion 2019.",
        "background": "At No More Exclusions we call upon government to end the power to exclude children from school after emerging from such an unprecedented period of upheaval!",
